Calculate the mean age in the stock and catch

Source: R/FLStock.R
meanage.Rd

Average age in the stock numbers or catch-at-age.

Usage

meanage(object)

meanageCatch(object)

Arguments

object

An age-structured FLStock object

Value

An FLQuant object

See also

FLComp

Author

The FLR Team

Examples

data(ple4)
meanage(ple4)
